{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99720-yiqi-zhizuo-qing-ning-zhi-ba","title":"一起制作青柠汁吧！","description":"八个孩子在烈日下玩耍。他们想从拉竹叔叔给他们的食谱中作一壶青柠汁。他们如何量成分？他们如何平均分饮料？让我们使用美味食谱介绍分数的概念吧！","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Niloufer Wadia"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99720-yiqi-zhizuo-qing-ning-zhi-ba"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/716367/size3/e97da48c8cd10ab3eb5854216b62b4a7.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/716367/size6/e97da48c8cd10ab3eb5854216b62b4a7.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67905/size6/6872c30286861fcd42e44f093d41b06c.jpg","text":"放学后，我们在菩提树树下玩耍。\n捉迷藏，毽子，跳皮筋，三个字，老鹰追小鸡等等。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67906/size6/b837eac080a7e35cabf8ba1dd29c6149.jpg","text":"拉竹叔叔的茶店就在树的附近。\n天气很热的时候，他会留下一壶青柠汁和杯子给我们。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67907/size6/17b42871f8f7a50ce239228a78b9dcd7.jpg","text":"我们如何将青柠汁平均分给我们八个人呢？\n阿曼的口袋里有一根绳子。我们将它剪成与壶里饮料高度相同的长度。","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67908/size6/6a3f0417a955208946e7e254af0c4c52.jpg","text":"我们将线对折。然后再将分成两半的线再对折两次。现在我们有八个相等的线了。\n我们将折叠的绳子放在茶壶的旁边，并在茶壶上标记相等的部分。","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67909/size6/96613cf40eef4889ccac6c8b7d0edc70.jpg","text":"曼努和莎拉一同提起了水壶，小心翼翼地将青柠汁倒入玻璃杯中。","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69347/size6/a4d866d1f6b6ec3188bfdd5f3948e5fd.jpg","text":"真美味，我们都想要更多。拉竹叔叔说：“你们可以再做一些。”\n“制作方法贴在板上。”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67912/size6/fedd8203183a37b627b353284943fe75.jpg","text":"青柠汁的做法\n十分之一的青柠汁\n十分之二的糖浆\n十分之七的冷水\n搅拌均匀便可享用。","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69346/size6/22c9f76d7d9404ac28b1fbf70ab395cc.jpg","text":"我们有水，糖浆和青柠汁，但我们不知道如何测量十分之一。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67913/size6/1eeb70be8ec4bee26608d4198cfe86e2.jpg","text":"古里亚说：“我们已经标上八个部分。 我们再标记两个就得出十个部分了。”\n阿鲁将青柠汁倒至第一个标记。我倒了两份糖浆，使混合物上升到第三个标记。曼努将冷水倒入第10个标记。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67914/size6/b0801c8cec79284553175ddfe4828a9c.jpg","text":"11/16","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67915/size6/0fcb27d0a49d0aa9b443277927a90a66.jpg","text":"我们倒了八杯青柠汁，还剩下一些青柠汁。我们把它倒入Raju Uncle的一大杯里。","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67916/size6/a1cfcd66b5fae10012e1c9910c70c84a.jpg","text":"拉竹叔叔说：“沙巴斯！这是我喝过最好喝的青柠汁了！但是，但是如果配上一些热腾腾的炸蔬菜就更美味了。”\n“万岁！ 谢谢你，拉竹叔叔！”","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67917/size6/13b534aaf609cfc46a370a440349191a.jpg","text":"四分之一。\n一半。\n半。\n满。\n充分。\n你有时会用这些词吗？","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67918/size6/de026386112e21993ebf3aeaab1e5924.jpg","text":"取出一整个柠檬，让大人把它切成八等份。用刀时小心。每一分都是一整个部分的其中之一。这些小部分称为分数。现在试试看把每一小部分放在一起，你就得出半个柠檬了。\n有多少个小部分呢？","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67919/size6/738cd1531fd402fb0802addb73d24bee.jpg","text":"给你的朋友四分之三的柠檬。\n她得到了几分？\n假如说你的兄弟想要半个柠檬。\n一半是多少分？\n八分之一= 1/8","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":40}}